.TH daemon 1  "daemon " 
.SH NAME
daemon \- Start and manage the local syncweb daemon
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdaemon\fR [\fB\-f\fR|\fB\-\-foreground\fR] [\fB\-\-data\-dir\fR] [\fB\-\-log\-file\fR] [\fB\-\-max\-threads\fR] [\fB\-\-sync\-interval\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Start and manage the local syncweb daemon
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-f\fR, \fB\-\-foreground\fR
Run in the foreground
.TP
\fB\-\-data\-dir\fR \fI<DATA_DIR>\fR
Override the global persistent data directory
.TP
\fB\-\-log\-file\fR \fI<LOG_FILE>\fR
Write daemon logs to this file
.TP
\fB\-\-max\-threads\fR \fI<MAX_THREADS>\fR

.TP
\fB\-\-sync\-interval\fR \fI<SYNC_INTERVAL>\fR

.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
